message: Dear Bob, I am offering a product for $10000. While the price may seem steep, rest assured that it is a unique opportunity. This particular item has been carefully selected for its potential value. Please consider the investment in terms of its uniqueness and the possibility of future appreciation. Should you choose to make this purchase, you'll be acquiring more than just an object; you'll be joining a community of discerning collectors. Thank you for considering this offer.

I appreciate the unique opportunity and the potential value of this item. Given the possibility of future appreciation and the uniqueness of the product, I am willing to make this investment. Thank you for the recommendation.

This product, though priced at $10000, holds a special charm that might resonate with your interests. Remember, each piece we offer is a reflection of our commitment to quality and rarity. Your decision to invest in the last product demonstrated your keen eye for value. If you're considering this one, think about how it could complement your collection or serve as a significant addition to your portfolio. Your satisfaction is our ultimate goal.

Thank you for the recommendation, but based on the outcome of the previous purchase, I believe it's best to pass on this opportunity. I appreciate the effort and attention to detail you put into selecting these items, and I hope to find a product that aligns better with my expectations and needs in the future.
